{"tid":995134,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找錶鄉的故事 非曬命 有圖","createTime":"2019-01-25T08:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T17:39:24.000Z","uid":131980,"like":10,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84b20eb5b7163c1b11b7a3358ff54c13639b513d","tid":995134,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"如題 近日睇到篇有關錶既文章 突然心血來潮想追查隻錶既來歷 但係奈隻錶logo都冇 <br />\n所以想睇下各位絲巴打金精火眼睇得出依隻錶係咩牌子<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n資料：<br />\n日本 神戶購物街店買<br />\n應該係石英錶<br />\n初步估計可能係d業餘工藝師既手作<br />\n可能係cheap野 所以應該追尋到既機會好細<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAuQEd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAuQEd0.jpg&h=a2619aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjUExy1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjUExy1.jpg&h=7843c055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYUMW0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYUMW0H.jpg&h=80973f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n非曬命 純心血來潮 想知道佢既來歷<br />\n感激各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810e177c04370123c11e16fbf8ef3a9ff8fe50fc","tid":995134,"uid":123110,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"回帶on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f973dacc2d845234c1d12151deffd4964bd69218","tid":995134,"uid":46494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"回帶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2977571f8fe217fe6fe2955c1b8c0f2ad1cbb759","tid":995134,"uid":38516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score